      </p>

      {/* ÊåâÈíÆÁªÑ */}
      <div
        className={`mt-10 flex gap-6 transition-opacity duration-1000 ${
          showButtons ? 'opacity-100' : 'opacity-0 pointer-events-none'
        }`}
      >
        <button className="bg-white/70 hover:bg-white/90 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow text-blue-700 font-semibold backdrop-blur">
          ÊâæÂ∑•‰Ωú
        </button>
